'''Disney Channel Portugal''' is Portuguese simulcast of '''[[Disney Channel]]'''. Broadcasts [[Disney Channel]], [[Disney XD (United States)|Disney XD]] and [[Disney Junior]] originals and non-originals. It was launched in November 2001.
